HEADWORD: Elutriation
<hw>E*lu`tri*a"tion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The process of
elutriating; a decanting or racking off by means of water, as finer
particles from heavier.</def>⟦br⟧
